Package de.humatic.mmj

Interface Summary
MidiListener Listener interface for incoming Midi data.
MidiSystemListener Notification interface to listen for changes in the Midi system like device attachment and removal.
 

Class Summary
CoreMidiDevice CoreMidiDevice is a descriptive structure providing information on MidiDevices.
MidiInput An opened Midi input from that the application reads MIDI by attaching itself as a MidiListener.
MidiOutput An opened Midi output to which the application sends Midi.
MidiSystem MidiSystem provides static methods to open Midi ports and to get information on a machine's MIDI system.
